Pengerusi Joo sudah balik.

68
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,100
Lambat awak balik.

69
00:03:47,125 --> 00:03:49,511
Penjenayah bagi kejadian parung
akan ditangkap tidak lama lagi.

70
00:03:50,715 --> 00:03:52,115
Awak sudah jumpa dia?

71
00:03:53,569 --> 00:03:54,969
Siapa dia?

72
00:03:55,564 --> 00:03:56,964
Tidak pasti lagi.

73
00:03:56,989 --> 00:03:59,049
